				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ice PBAOE is really powerfull but needs alot of backup : 2 ice wizards + a mind sorceror + 4 tanks + 2 healers + minstrel + theurgist + 2 rogues + some more makes a great combo. ( yes you need 2 groups to get that )
<br />

<br />
It all comes down to have to right support, and for ice wizards to be effective you need almost 2 full groups to provide the needed support.  If you have that support and the team works well together you are devastating.
<br />

<br />
If you dont have the needed support you are easy RP.
<br />

<br />
Fire wizards arent that bad, they can snipe pretty well with there bolts, but that wont work in large scale RVR.
<br />

<br />
The Fire wizard is good at ranged damage, and probably the best ranged damage dealer of all realms, BUT they dont have any utility and are easy targets for rogue classes.
<br />

<br />
The wizard community is waiting until the earth line gets fixed and maybe we get some utility from that.
<br />

<br />
Until then I sugest to play a smite cleric.
<br />

<br />
You are lvl 24 go play in the 1st Battleground and see what happens.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
